{"tid":2373160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩度檢測假陰性 患者轟採樣馬虎","createTime":"2021-01-20T08:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T14:41:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61b594034dd9db271c89446c7d432f582359e3db","tid":2373160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/QLSPKVKMWREZHJHL5FOPQQLUKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FQLSPKVKMWREZHJHL5FOPQQLUKU%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=0f26335a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FQLSPKVKMWREZHJHL5FOPQQLUKU%2F&h=7cd1306c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/QLSPKVKMWREZHJHL5FOPQQLUKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩度檢測假陰性 患者轟採樣馬虎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RXFVvjjEvSWae1lMp_splO58hEU=/1000x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UZPUDFH4W5DLZPRCZNSSFKGA2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRXFVvjjEvSWae1lMp_splO58hEU%3D%2F1000x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUZPUDFH4W5DLZPRCZNSSFKGA2Y.jpg&h=4b538dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨晚確診的尼泊爾裔患者指同日下午到採樣站檢測的結果是呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府擴大強制檢測範圍，但檢測服務的準確度卻成疑。有患者因身體不適先後兩度到政府社區檢測中心及採樣站檢測，結果均呈陰性，惟不適情況加劇，至昨晚再到廣華醫院求診，結果醫院檢測呈陽性，跟進檢查更發現病況嚴重、肺炎惡化。患者在醫院聞着氧氣受訪，稱幸好沒有相信檢測中心及採樣站的結果，否則病情或已更嚴重，甚至有機會傳染妻兒。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政府又轉軚 年宵縮水復活  桃花大王：班仆街坐住個腦<br />\n<br />\n該名尼泊爾裔的Dilip表示，上周初開始頭痛，服用止痛藥數天後到私家診所求醫，當時沒安排檢測。至上周五，他的體溫介乎正常至輕燒之間，遂到由金域承辦的油麻地社區檢測中心做測試，結果呈陰性。惟不適的感覺持續加劇，直至昨日，他同住的親人確診武漢肺炎後，他下午到玉器街的採樣站接受檢測，結果同樣呈陰性；但晚上他因病痛難當，召救護車到廣華醫院就診，篩檢樣本證實感染武肺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家不排除同類個案再現<br />\n<br />\nDilip引述醫護表示，他的病情嚴重，需要聞氧氣，肺炎範圍大，已服用抗病毒藥物。他說難以接受昨日下午的檢測結果呈陰性，但晚上到醫院檢測卻改為確診，質疑採樣人員取樣馬虎，沒有把拭子放到鼻腔及口腔深處，「我完全沒感到痛楚及不適，當時已覺得很奇怪」。他幸好有叫救護車送院治療，否則不但延誤病情，妻兒受感染風險機會也更高。他希望地區的採樣服務能更加認真，政府做好監察工作。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：遍地爆 政府「獨厚」油麻地  連日稱情況嚴峻 實際只佔個案兩成<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超相信，患者兩次社區檢測的採樣位置及質素或有偏差，例如沒有觸及病毒量較高的位置，亦可能是病毒量集中於下呼吸道，故鼻腔及口腔拭子的病毒量不足以呈陽性反應。他指隨着社區檢測數量不斷增加，不排除再出現同類個案。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會幹事彭鴻昌相信採樣站的檢測出現「假陰性」，認為政府應就事件調查。"},{"pid":"5f521789f65689a34e743e56e2ff76f831e6c38c","tid":2373160,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有邊樣野唔馬虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b73beffba30e9885464f27cf9fab16088e8928","tid":2373160,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5f521789f65689a34e743e56e2ff76f831e6c38c","tid":2373160,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有邊樣野唔馬虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"推行國安法<br />\n檢控暴動罪"},{"pid":"ed2e48d6802695ad65c802c6049e1552a387e430","tid":2373160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"唔call白車去醫院就變咗私烟"},{"pid":"57b7456d8f6b1194a15ff1c0fbd109a74eee7495","tid":2373160,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b73beffba30e9885464f27cf9fab16088e8928","tid":2373160,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5f521789f65689a34e743e56e2ff76f831e6c38c","tid":2373160,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有邊樣野唔馬虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"推行國安法<br />\n檢控暴動罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"其實都係馬虎<br />\n只不過因為球證旁證足總都係佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da35fcb94624457c9fe031641fd2edcac7cbcb1a","tid":2373160,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"分分鐘有好多隱形傳播都係因為驗左假陰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19935fb497a9068cb7768cbc3aaf165aab9e0fe6","tid":2373160,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:15:57.000Z","msg":"支那驗11次先確診<br />\n有排都未破紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0821d8394b76bed4a1d709f5b55ccfea2602d1f","tid":2373160,"uid":97078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"係咪因為了鼻比深喉痰無咁準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b534b7541b03e31f960390818ccc687bf5bfb345","tid":2373160,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0821d8394b76bed4a1d709f5b55ccfea2602d1f","tid":2373160,"uid":97078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"係咪因為了鼻比深喉痰無咁準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔係 係因為係金域"},{"pid":"6263bd2b6b8b06b0f78a816eea2294b6f68ba659","tid":2373160,"uid":48193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"其實幫人驗班撚樣咪又係臨時拉夫<br />\n真有技術有能力有知識去探樣個班比人拉哂去抗疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n檢疫中心淨返咩人大家心照"},{"pid":"22c628f66e8c9ea0b0fa0cd0a5f91fc7eac95e68","tid":2373160,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"是是但但"},{"pid":"170e465cb9edd806a8ef4194c0659c67e69934f0","tid":2373160,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"用強國檢查劑係咁上下"},{"pid":"b6d017bfc417db19a6ca20bd404e0531fef3d505","tid":2373160,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b534b7541b03e31f960390818ccc687bf5bfb345","tid":2373160,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0821d8394b76